_sText:
This Map was modify from mg_yuras_multigames. 

It's a funny zombie mod map with no any plugin!

Its only have a zombie mod. 
randomly swap team to being zombie or human.

Human: survive 3 minutes. or kill all zombies
Zombie: kill all human.

Human have a lot of place to defend zombies. 
such as a breakable wood place , a hidden place.
a place have secret weapon for human!

Zombie have 2 hp recover place, a smoke secret place!
oh! when you pick up weapon,you will forced to use knife!
